{"tid":1364514,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(大家請放心) 宗教活動不會構成非法集會，亦無需申請，絕對合法","createTime":"2019-07-25T11:17:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T13:23:05.000Z","uid":222970,"like":48,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"01132677b7716809aea8d26db23c376210f38ca2","tid":1364514,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T11:17:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yLCXL0D.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyLCXL0D.png&h=c9cd6a19&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">各位教徒，如果怕比黑警屈你係非法集結 <br />\n建議大家將電話wallpaper轉d十字架 佢咁屈唔到你<br />\n或者print定d耶穌相係袋到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n根據《 公安條例》，&quot;集 會&quot;的定義是任何經召集或組織而舉行的聚集或集結是以討論一般公眾人士感興趣或關注 的問題或事項為目的，或是以在該等問題或事項上表達意見為目的， 而當中有人為以上目的而在現<br />\n場負責控制或領導。<br />\n不過，為以下目的 而召集的聚集則不包括在內<span style=\"color: red;\">：社交、康樂、文化、學術、教育、宗教 、慈善、專業、業務或商業性質的聚集、為殯殮而舉行的聚集</span>、為任 何公共機構而舉行的聚集、為執行或行使任何條例所委以或授與的職 責或權力而舉行的聚集。&quot;"},{"pid":"9dfa2e9f9f3f5124bd92c05ec6599672b2de650b","tid":1364514,"uid":39010,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T11:19:00.000Z","msg":"信一日啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3e42ae98c267017a26b7be083b00c625160fd6e","tid":1364514,"uid":273621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T11:20:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1364366/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1364366/page/1</a><br />\n真係要"},{"pid":"13747e5f6e8594edc27b20b6611918847e9498bd","tid":1364514,"uid":222970,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T11:20:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HjUrEn8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHjUrEn8.png&h=d6e3f14d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"